Nicholas D'Agosto https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicholas_D%27Agosto 0 Nicholas D'Agosto (born April 17, 1980) is an American actor. He is known for being the lead of Final Destination 5 and his recurring roles in Heroes and The Office. He starred in the Showtime series Masters of Sex and the Fox series Gotham. D'Agosto also stars in NBC's show Trial Error which finished airing its second season in October 2018. Nicholas_D'Agosto ( born April_17_,_1980 ) is an_American_actor .
